unrise]]\n| 4\n| 1\n| 5\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#f0f0f0;\"\n| [[54th National Hockey League All-Star Game|2007]]\n| [[Dallas Stars|Dallas]]\n| 1\n| 1\n| 2\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| [[56th National Hockey League All-Star Game|2008]]\n| [[Atlanta Thrashers|Atlanta]]\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#f0f0f0;\"\n| [[57th National Hockey League All-Star Game|2009]]\n| [[Montreal Canadiens|Montreal]]\n| 1\n| 0\n| 1\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#e0e0e0;\"\n! colspan=3 | All-Star totals\n! 6\n! 2\n! 8\n|}\n\n==Awards and achievements==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! Award\n! Year\n!\n|- ALIGN=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#e0e0e0\"\n| colspan=\"3\" | [[Alberta Midget Hockey League|AMHL]]\n|-\n| [[Telus Cup|Air Canada Cup]] bronze medal \n| [[1997 Air Canada Cup|1997]], [[1998 Air Canada Cup|1998]]\n|\n|-\n| Harry Allen Memorial Trophy (Top scorer) \n| 1998\n|\n|-\n| Air Canada Cup MVP \n| 1998\n|\n|- ALIGN=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#e0e0e0\"\n| colspan=\"3\" | [[Alberta Junior Hockey League|AJHL]]\n|-\n| Player of the Year \n| 1999\n|\n|-\n| [[Canadian Junior A Hockey League|CJHL]] Player of the Year \n| 1999\n|\n|- ALIGN=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#e0e0e0\"\n| colspan=\"3\" | [[NCAA Division I men's ice hockey|College]]\n|-\n| All-[[Western Collegiate Hockey Association|WCHA]] [[List of All-WCHA Hockey Teams#Rookie Team|Rookie Team]]\n| [[1999\u20132000 NCAA Division I men's ice hockey season|2000]]\n|\n|-\n| All-[[Western Collegiate Hockey Association|WCHA]] [[List of All-WCHA Hockey Teams#First Team|First Team]]\n| 2000\n|\n|-\n| [[Western Collegiate Hockey Association|WCHA]] [[Western Collegiate Hockey Association men's individual awards#Rookie of the Year|Rookie of the Year]]\n| 2000\n|\n|-\n| [[American Hockey Coaches Association|AHCA]] [[List of Division I AHCA All-American Teams|West Second-Team All-American]]\n| 2000\n|\n|-\n| All-[[Western Collegiate Hockey Association|WCHA]] [[List of All-WCHA Hockey Team